  <name>Fulgur</name>
  <icon type="stock">app.fulgur.fulgur</icon>
  <summary>Lightning-fast, fully themable, multiplatform text editor with secure file synchronization</summary>

  <developer id="app.fulgur">
    <name>PRRPCHT</name>
  </developer>

  <description>
    <p>
      Fulgur is a GPU-accelerated, open-source text editor built with Rust and GPUI.
    </p>
    <p>
      It supports 50+ languages, first-class Markdown editing, and runs on Windows, macOS, and Linux.
    </p>
    <p>
      Fulgur works offline by default and can securely sync text files between devices with end-to-end encryption via Fulgurant.
    </p>
  </description>

